<HEADLINE> Lights-Camera-Action at White House </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- Lighting and sound technicians swarmed the  
West Wing of the White House on Thursday, getting things just right 
for the newest installment of President Clinton's campaign against 
youth violence. 
</P>
<P>
	The president, first lady Hillary Rodham Clinton and 40  
