his Joint Chiefs of Staff at a critical juncture in the campaign 
against Kosovo. 
</P>
<P>
	Why such a fuss by the network?  
</P>
<P>
	``They're very particular about their lighting,'' one White  
House aide whispered. 
  	   	
</P>
