<P>
 *Four months ended May 29: 
</P>
<P>
	Same-store sales rose 4 percent.  
</P>
<P>
	Total sales were $5.04 billion, up 9.2 percent from $4.61  
billion. (Total sales include the revenues from the direct-seller 
Fingerhut, which was acquired in March).	
