<HEADLINE> 4 Fullerton BB Players Suspended </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	FULLERTON, Calif. (AP) -- Four Cal State-Fullerton baseball  
players were suspended after being arrested for throwing rocks off 
a building in South Bend, Ind. 
</P>
<P>
	Pitchers Adam Johnson and Marco Hanlon, second baseman David  
Bacani and shortstop Chad Olszanski were sent home, coach George 
Horton said, and will miss the NCAA tournament regional at Ohio 
