Exchange, boosted by a healthy opening on Wall Street. 
</P>
<P>
	The blue chip Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-Share Index  
finished up 46.40 points, or 0.7 percent, at 6,348.60. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 852.3 million shares, compared with 942.6  
